General.Description: MaidSafe Coin or MAID is the World's First Autonomous Data Network. Built as the fully decentralized platform, MaidSafe enable to build decentralized applications and the network. This network is the place where individual users who contribute storage, computing power and bandwidth to form a world-wide autonomous system.
General.Features: MaidSafe network provides static and dynamic data as well as communications with efficient features. For example, the clients can code on their own and can cryptographically sign. In the case the network cannot decrypt any of the data, the users can be helped from decentralized server such as diffent tasks of today's httpd, ssh, scp, ftp, smtp, pop3, imap etc.
General.Technology: MaidSafe has been developed with all the updated technologies to build the Secure Access for Everyone (SAFE) network which can be trustful as a fully distributed data management service. There are some figures about the technical data of MAID such a market capability is more than $330 million, the volume each 24 hours is $4.453.970 USD.
